 That install applies to "Roguecraft DX" © 2026 Badger Punch Games
 Slave requires WHDLoad V17+.
 Game needs 2Mb Chipmem, 4Mb fastmem
 It can be quit by pressing F10 (key can be changed with Tooltype "QuitKey=").

 If you have problems with this installation please try and get a newer
 version of this package from the WHDLoad WWW-Page. If that doesn't help try
 some Tooltypes like NOCACHE, NOAUTOVEC, NOVBRMOVE, NOMMU, PAL or NTSC. If
 that also fails, please inform the author via the Bug-Report-Form which
 can be accessed on the WHDLoad WWW-Page or create a mantis issue directly
 at http://mantis.whdload.de

	for full WHDLoad package and other installs refer to:
		http://www.whdload.de/
	or	aminet:dev/misc/whdload#?
	and	aminet:game/patch/

 History
 -------

 version 1.1 () done by JOTD:
 - fixed color burst bit in copperlists
 - file "RoguecraftDX.exe" can be packed using propack or imploder data
 
 version 1.0 (05.06.2026) done by JOTD/Arise from decay
 - trainer added (no scores or achievements will be saved when trainer is enabled :)

 This .slave replaces the official .slave provided by the game developpers.
 It has been created using jotd whd_slave_resourcer.py resourcing tool.
